title: Blue Moon - A One and a Two...
description:
'Blue Moon - A One and a Two'

The Adventures of Lyssa and the Pirates

Aeon, 1995, 69 pages

Written, Drawn and Quartered by Charlie Wise

...what thirty-two year old woman wouldn't want to walk through a door and wind up the captain of a pirate ship?

---------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This guys art reminds me a lot of Phil Foglio. Lines are a little thicker, and there's a bit less background detail, but there's definitely a lot of similarities. ...ah! They worked together on a Xxxenophiles Presents book. Huh.
